    public class LeoRemoteAnnotator

    Create an annotator that sends each CAS received to a remote service. Remote annotators cannot have more than one instance per asynchronous pipeline so the number of instances cannot be set. User: Thomas Ginter Date: 8/8/14 Time: 12:55
